<!-- 
This is the Tomcat context file which installs XProc-Z as the ROOT servlet.
To specify additional parameters, or set a different main pipeline, override this "ROOT" context file 
by mounting a replacement file, e.g. using docker run: 
docker run -p 8080:8080 -v /path/to/custom-context.xml:/usr/local/tomcat/conf/Catalina/localhost/ROOT.xml xproc-z
To provide a different pipeline, and to provide supporting data, XSLT, etc, you can mount another 
directory to replace the /var/lib/xproc-z/ folder in the container. e.g.
docker run -p 8080:8080 -v /path/to/my-xproc-and-related-data:/var/lib/xproc-z xproc-z
-->
<Context docBase="/usr/local/xproc-z.war">
